verbose_text: CAP1 expression was significantly associated with the histological grade (P = 0.010) and Ki-67 expression (P < 0.001), whereas there was no correlation observed with the FIGO stage (P = 0.477), menopause (P = 0.395), ascites (P = 0.666), lymph node status (P = 0.209), malignant tumor cells (P = 0.472), metastases to other organs (P = 0.666), age (P = 0.775) and histologic subtype (P = 0.071).
